{
  "id": "adv_event_2109_01_02",
  "title": "私じゃダメ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "愛、一人だけ動きが遅れてるわよ！\n気を抜かないで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ you’re the only one moving slower!\nKeep concentrating!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい！　すみません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-okay! I’m sorry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.133333333333334,
      "endTime": 7.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "もっと集中しなさい！\n今の所、もう一度最初から！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You need to concentrate more!\nDo this bit again from the start!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8,
      "endTime": 12.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\n1、2、3、ここでステップ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!\n1‚ 2‚ 3‚ step here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.366666666666667,
      "endTime": 16.333333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、間違えた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I got it wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6,
      "endTime": 19.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "愛……\nもういいわ。少し休憩にしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai…\nEnough for now. Let’s take a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.7,
      "endTime": 24.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2066.6666666666665
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "すみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.666666666666668,
      "endTime": 27.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "今日の愛は全然集中出来てなかったね～\n大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You weren’t able to concentrate at all today‚ Ai.\nAre you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.566666666666666,
      "endTime": 34.58956502278645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "……私なんかがあの曲を歌っていいのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is it really okay for someone like me to sing that song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.766666666666666,
      "endTime": 38.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "あの曲って、The Last Chanceのこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That song? You mean The Last Chance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.13333333333333,
      "endTime": 42.32573693593343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "でもあれって愛の大好きな曲だよね？\n愛は歌いたくないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t that a song you really love?\nDon’t you want to sing it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 48.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "大好きだから歌うのが怖いんだよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I love it‚ but I’m scared of singing it‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.233333333333334,
      "endTime": 50.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "私はあの曲にふさわしくないから……\nこんなダメダメな私じゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "because I’m not right for that song…\nI’m just not good enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.233333333333334,
      "endTime": 57.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、この前のライブで怒られたことを\nまだ気にしてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you still worrying about getting scolded\nafter the last live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.56666666666667,
      "endTime": 62.966666666666654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "だって、私はいつも莉央さんの足を引っ張って\n迷惑掛けてばかりで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’m always holding Rio-san back and causing\nher trouble…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.166666666666664,
      "endTime": 68.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "こんな私がリズノワの一員なんて\n最初から荷が重かったんだよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For me to be a member of LizNoir\nwas too heavy a load from the start…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.16666666666667,
      "endTime": 75.43333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ライブのミスと新曲のプレッシャーで\n思いっきりマイナス思考になっちゃってるね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With your mistakes on stage and the pressure of a new song‚\nyou’ve got into a totally negative mindset…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.63333333333334,
      "endTime": 81.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "しょうがないなあ～。LizNoir真のリーダー\n赤崎こころが一肌脱ぎますか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It can’t be helped. I guess as the real leader of LizNoir‚\nI’ll have to lend you a hand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.86666666666666,
      "endTime": 88.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "合宿？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A camp?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 92.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "そうです！　みんなで合宿するんですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! We’re all going to do a camp.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 95.85424025853474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "最近なんだかカリカリしちゃってカルシウム不足な方も\nいるようだし、ここは環境を変えて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One of us has been a bit calcitrant and calcium-deficient lately‚\nso that’s why we should change the environment…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 102.32288239353392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "誰のことを言っているのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who are you talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 104.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "それはもちろん、莉……愛ちゃんですよぉ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ that would be Ri… I mean‚ Ai-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.1,
      "endTime": 109.41000022888183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6,
      "endTime": 110.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "今、妙な間があったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s with the pause just now…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 113.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "僕は合宿してもいいよ\nたまには環境を変えるのもいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t mind doing a camp.\nIt’s good to have a change of scene from time to time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3,
      "endTime": 118.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "葵までそんな気軽に言って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even you‚ Aoi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9,
      "endTime": 121.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "そもそもスケジュールはどうするつもり？\n仕事があるから何泊も出来ないでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But what are we going to do about the schedule?\nWe have work to do‚ so we can’t spend many nights on this‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9,
      "endTime": 127.19999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "サニピが合宿した時は、{user}さんが\n頑張ってスケジュール調整したらしいですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Apparently‚ when Sunny Peace did their camp‚ {user}-san\nstretched to adjust their schedule.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.43333333333334,
      "endTime": 132.9394333203631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2109_01_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "だから今回も{user}さんに\n頑張ってもらえばきっと大丈夫です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So if we get {user}-san to do his best again‚\nit’s sure to be fine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.13333333333333,
      "endTime": 137.6868692894777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
